OL,3,CMan treated in hospital after being
OL,4,Cshot in leg
OL,6,FA man has been treated in hospital
OL,7,Fafter he was shot in the leg in Co
OL,8,FDown.
OL,10,FPolice said the victim of the shooting
OL,11,Fin Bangor would be left with "lasting
OL,12,Fphysical and emotional trauma".
OL,14,FDetectives are appealing for
OL,15,Finformation about the incident that
OL,16,Foccurred in the Bloomfield Road area
OL,17,Fat around 10.40pm on Tuesday.
OL,26,@sD@^OUtD@^O]
