OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1778691956
OL,3,CMan treated in hospital after being
OL,4,Cshot in leg
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Officers
OL,7,Falong with colleagues from the
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,9,Fattended and the man was taken to
OL,10,Fhospital for treatment to a gunshot
OL,11,Fwound to his leg.
OL,13,F"Although his injuries are thankfully
OL,14,Fnot likely to be fatal, they are
OL,15,Fsevere and will no doubt leave him
OL,16,Fwith lasting physical and emotional
OL,17,Ftrauma.
OL,26,@nD@[OUuD@AOU
