OL,3,CMan treated in hospital after being
OL,4,Cshot in leg
OL,6,F"This attack has caused fear and
OL,7,Fdisruption in the very community those
OL,8,Fresponsible for this criminal act
OL,9,Fclaim to protect and there is no
OL,10,Fjustification for this violence."
OL,12,FPolice have appealed for anyone with
OL,13,Finformation to contact them on 101,
OL,14,Fquoting reference number 1763 12/05/26.
